[[Back to start|Start]]

:: Character Generation

{set _temp = $character}
{computed _points = 15 + (5 * $character.level) - _temp.strength - _temp.dexterity - _temp.intelligence}

### Debug
{button $character.level++}Level Up!{/button}

### Character Generation

| Stat | Base | | New | |
| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Strength | {$character.strength} | → | {_temp.strength} | {if _temp.strength > $character.strength}{button _temp.strength--}-{/button}{/if} {if _points > 0}{button _temp.strength++}+{/button}{/if} |
| Dexterity | {$character.dexterity} | → | {_temp.dexterity} | {if _temp.dexterity > $character.dexterity}{button _temp.dexterity--}-{/button}{/if} {if _points > 0}{button _temp.dexterity++}+{/button}{/if} |
| Intelligence | {$character.intelligence} | → | {_temp.intelligence} | {if _temp.intelligence > $character.intelligence}{button _temp.intelligence--}-{/button}{/if} {if _points > 0}{button _temp.intelligence++}+{/button}{/if} |

{if _points > 0}**Points remaining:** {_points}{/if}
{if _points == 0}**All points allocated**{/if}

{if _points == 0}
{button $character = _temp}Confirm{/button} [[Go Back -> Start]]
{/if}